&lt;p&gt;在禁用半主机模式后，对于标准 C 库一般会重定义实现以下 &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9kZXZlbG9wZXIuYXJtLmNvbS9kb2N1bWVudGF0aW9uL2R1aTAyMzIvYi90aGUtYy1hbmQtYy0tLWxpYnJhcmllcy90YWlsb3JpbmctdGhlLWlucHV0LW91dHB1dC1mdW5jdGlvbnMvZGVwZW5kZW5jaWVzLW9uLWxvdy1sZXZlbC1mdW5jdGlvbnM/bGFuZz1lbg==&#34;&gt;Dependencies on low-level functions&lt;/span&gt; 函数：&lt;/p&gt;
